== 製作 ==
2017年1月25日，[[環球影業|環球影業]]宣佈製作《[[歡樂好聲音|歡樂好聲音]]》續集<ref>{{cite news|last1=Busch|first1=Anita|title=Universal Dates ‘Sing 2’ & ‘Minions 2,’ Moves ‘Secret Life of Pets 2’ Back A Year|url=http://deadline.com/2017/01/minions-2-sing-2-secret-life-of-pets-2-release-dates-1201894439/|accessdate=2017-01-26|work=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|date=2017-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170127015355/http://deadline.com/2017/01/minions-2-sing-2-secret-life-of-pets-2-release-dates-1201894439/|archive-date=2017-01-27|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Chitwood|first1=Adam|title=‘Sing 2’ and ‘Minions 2’ Get 2020 Release Dates; ‘Secret Life of Pets 2’ Pushed Back|url=https://collider.com/minions-2-release-date-sing-2/|date=2017-01-26|work=[[Collider|Collider]]|accessdate=2017-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170126181446/http://collider.com/minions-2-release-date-sing-2/|archive-date=2017-01-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2019年4月12日，確認[[葛斯·詹寧斯|葛斯·詹寧斯]]回歸執導電影，而[[馬修·麥康納|馬修·麥康納]]、[[瑞絲·薇斯朋|瑞絲·薇斯朋]]、[[史嘉蕾·喬韓森|史嘉蕾·喬韓森]]、[[泰隆·艾格頓|泰隆·艾格頓]]、{{le|尼克·克羅爾|Nick Kroll}}和[[托蕾·凱莉|托蕾·凱莉]]回歸聲演各自的角色<ref>{{cite news|last1=D'Alessandro|first1=Anthony|title=‘Sing 2’ To Croon Summer 2021; ‘The Croods 2’ Moves To Holiday Season 2020|url=https://deadline.com/2019/04/sing-2-croods-2-release-date-changes-1202594951/|date=2019-04-12|work=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|accessdate=2019-04-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190828024514/https://deadline.com/2019/04/sing-2-croods-2-release-date-changes-1202594951/|archive-date=2019-08-28|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2020年12月，宣佈[[博诺|博诺]]、[[菲瑞·威廉斯|菲瑞·威廉斯]]、[[海爾希_(歌手)|海爾希]]、[[巴比·卡納佛|巴比·卡納佛]]、[[莉蒂西亞·萊特|莉蒂西亞·萊特]]、[[艾瑞克·安德烈|艾瑞克·安德烈]]和[[雀兒喜·柏瑞蒂|雀兒喜·柏瑞蒂]]加盟配音陣容<ref>{{cite news|last1=D'Alessandro|first1=Anthony|title=U2’s Bono, Pharrell Williams, Halsey Join Illumination/Universal’s Animated Film ‘Sing 2’|url=https://deadline.com/2020/12/bono-u2-pharrell-williams-halsey-matthew-mcconaughey-reese-witherspoon-sing-2-illumination-entertainment-animated-film-1234659993/|date=2020-12-21|work=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|accessdate=2020-12-22|archive-date=2021-02-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210205171042/https://deadline.com/2020/12/bono-u2-pharrell-williams-halsey-matthew-mcconaughey-reese-witherspoon-sing-2-illumination-entertainment-animated-film-1234659993/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

