《歡樂好聲音2》由[[環球影業|環球影業]]於2021年12月22日在美國上映<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2020/04/minions-the-rise-of-gru-sing-2-wicked-release-date-change-global-international-box-office-coronavirus-1202897417/|title=‘Minions: The Rise Of Gru’, ‘Sing 2’ Set New 2021 Release Dates; ‘Wicked’ Still Brewing Slot|last=Tartaglione|first=Nancy|date=2020-04-01|website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|access-date=2020-04-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200401205258/https://deadline.com/2020/04/minions-the-rise-of-gru-sing-2-wicked-release-date-change-global-international-box-office-coronavirus-1202897417/|archive-date=2020-04-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此前，上映日期曾定於2020年12月25日及2021年7月2日<ref name="THR">{{cite news|last=Kilday|first=Gregg|title=‘Sing ’Sequel Coming From Illumination and Universal|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/sing-sequel-coming-illumination-universal-968750|accessdate=2017-01-25|work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|date=2017-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180622140201/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/sing-sequel-coming-illumination-universal-968750|archive-date=2018-06-22|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=D'Alessandro|first=Anthony|title=‘Sing 2’ To Croon Summer 2021; ‘The Croods 2’ Moves To Holiday Season 2020|url=https://deadline.com/2019/04/sing-2-croods-2-release-date-changes-1202594951/|accessdate=2019-04-12|work=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|date=2019-04-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190828024514/https://deadline.com/2019/04/sing-2-croods-2-release-date-changes-1202594951/|archive-date=2019-08-28|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

